text: It’s the rudest cashier I ever met. Saw she literally shouted at small boy while he was paying …PLASTIC?… abt 3 times as the boy mother was not there. Is this a Singapore service nowadays. To the staff, if you not happy working, pls don’t spoilt the company reputation Don’t  throw your tantrum to the customers. You  don’t have to scare the little kid.. If this happened to my child, I would shout at her and make a scene.and demand for the apology. Shame to the company to have staff like that.

Regular at this Bukit Gombak Outlet, nice staff except for one indian lady who shouted at me when I put purchase in my own bag 1st. Ok my fault although I have done this many2 times.  Doesn't have to scold me and she became
Worst when I commented on how she just dump all my food purchase in the bag.
I asked her colleague if she is having menses.
If you are using your own bag, you have to pack your own purchased items into your own bag yourself, the cashier won't assist you. That's a first for me.
Many people are there as it cheap & my mum want to buy some stuff there too before going home
Item very cheap and price reasonable.
